1. Moj *biznis* raste iz dana u dan. (My *business* is growing day by day.)
2. On je veoma uspešan u *biznisu*. (He is very successful in *business*.)
3. Upravljanje *biznisom* zahteva veliku odgovornost. (Managing a *business* requires great responsibility.)
4. Naš *biznis* se bavi proizvodnjom kvalitetnih proizvoda. (Our *business* is involved in producing high-quality products.)
5. *Biznis* plan treba pažljivo razmotriti pre pokretanja novog posla. (A *business* plan should be carefully considered before starting a new venture.)
6. Njihov *biznis* je propao zbog loše finansijske situacije. (Their *business* failed due to poor financial conditions.)
7. Novi *biznis* će im doneti mnogo novca. (The new *business* will bring them a lot of money.)
8. Moram da putujem mnogo zbog *biznisa*. (I have to travel a lot because of *business*.)
9. Oni su uložili mnogo novca u svoj *biznis*. (They invested a lot of money in their *business*.)
10. *Biznis* model kompanije treba da bude održiv na duge staze. (The company's *business* model should be sustainable in the long run.)